<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 12:21:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>短缺是铜价上涨至新高的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shortages-key-coppers-upward-price-trajectory-new-peaks-2024-04-23/</link><description>未来几个月出现的短缺预计将维持铜价上涨至每吨 10,000 美元心理关口的上涨势头。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:53:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shortages-key-coppers-upward-price-trajectory-new-peaks-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>受 Thom Browne 品牌拖累，Zegna 第一季度收入下降 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/revenues-zegna-drop-5-q1-dragged-by-thom-browne-brand-2024-04-23/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团 Ermenegildo Zegna 周二公布，第一季度有机收入下降 5.3%（不包括 Tom Ford Fashion），主要是由于 Thom Browne 品牌销售额下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:15:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/revenues-zegna-drop-5-q1-dragged-by-thom-browne-brand-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>期待已久的对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的援助即将通过美国国会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/long-awaited-aid-ukraine-israel-taiwan-poised-pass-us-congress-2024-04-23/</link><description>众议院突然结束了长达数月的僵局，并在罕见的周六会议上批准了援助，本周，向乌克兰、以色列和台湾提供的数十亿美元的对外援助应该会轻松获得美国参议院的批准。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:06:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/long-awaited-aid-ukraine-israel-taiwan-poised-pass-us-congress-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特斯拉报告重挫，欧洲业务好转</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>奇瑞与 B-ON 组建电动货车合资公司，面向欧洲和北美市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chery-b-on-form-electric-vans-jv-europe-namerica-2024-04-23/</link><description>B-ON 和中国奇瑞 (CHERY.UL) 周二宣布成立电动货车合资企业，这家欧洲生产商将获得资金和奇瑞的制造基地，同时这家中国汽车制造商也能进入欧洲和美国市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:42:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chery-b-on-form-electric-vans-jv-europe-namerica-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国官员称，尽管美国“干涉”，中美关系仍保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-us-relations-stable-despite-us-interference-chinese-official-says-2024-04-23/</link><description>中国外交部官员在美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯访问之前表示，尽管美国的行动损害了中国的利益，但北京和华盛顿之间的关系正在稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-us-relations-stable-despite-us-interference-chinese-official-says-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>Telegram创始人表示，自苹果搬迁以来，中国下载量并未下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/telegram-founder-says-china-downloads-have-not-fallen-since-apple-move-2024-04-23/</link><description>Telegram 亿万富翁创始人兼首席执行官帕维尔·杜罗夫 (Pavel Durov) 表示，苹果上周从中国应用商店下架这款聊天应用的举动并没有导致中国下载量的任何下降，反而批评了苹果的“围墙花园”应用政策。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/telegram-founder-says-china-downloads-have-not-fallen-since-apple-move-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通中国任命新任中国证券部门负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-china-names-new-heads-china-investment-banking-arm-2024-04-23/</link><description>路透社查阅并得到公司发言人证实的一份公司备忘录显示，摩根大通任命陆芳为其中国证券部门董事会主席，接替前任主席朴朴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-china-names-new-heads-china-investment-banking-arm-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉股价在季度业绩公布前小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-edge-higher-ahead-quarterly-results-2024-04-23/</link><description>特斯拉股价周二在电动汽车制造商第一季度业绩公布之前小幅走高，分析师预计毛利率将创下六年多来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-edge-higher-ahead-quarterly-results-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示苹果第一季度智能手机在中国出货量暴跌19%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-q1-phone-sales-china-fall-191-huaweis-up-70-2024-04-23/</link><description>市场数据显示，由于华为(HWT.UL)在高端市场推出新产品而受到打击，苹果公司今年第一季度在中国的智能手机出货量暴跌19%，为2020年以来最差表现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-q1-phone-sales-china-fall-191-huaweis-up-70-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军上将称，鉴于“经济衰退”，中国的军费开支令人担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-military-spending-concerning-given-failing-economy-us-admiral-says-2024-04-23/</link><description>美国印太司令部司令周二表示，鉴于中国经济“衰退”，中国国防开支的增加令人担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:58:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-military-spending-concerning-given-failing-economy-us-admiral-says-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟议会工作人员因为中国从事间谍活动在德国被捕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/report-staffer-germanys-afd-arrested-over-china-espionage-suspicions-2024-04-23/</link><description>欧洲议会极右翼德国另类选择党一名议员的一名助手因涉嫌为中国从事“特别严重”间谍活动而在德国被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:51:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/report-staffer-germanys-afd-arrested-over-china-espionage-suspicions-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>日本电产（Nidec）公布意外季度亏损，因中国电动汽车战争中的重组成本而受到打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nidec-posts-quarterly-loss-hit-by-restructuring-costs-2024-04-23/</link><description>日本电动机制造商日本电产周二公布，由于为应对中国电动汽车市场激烈的价格竞争而采取重组措施的成本，导致一月至三月季度出现意外运营亏损。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nidec-posts-quarterly-loss-hit-by-restructuring-costs-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国将修订统计法打击数据造假</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-revise-statistics-law-fight-data-fraud-2024-04-23/</link><description>官方媒体新华社周二表示，由于人们对世界第二大经济体数据的可靠性表示怀疑，中国将修改统计法，以打击持续存在的数据欺诈行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-revise-statistics-law-fight-data-fraud-2024-04-23/</guid></item><item><title>联合国气象机构称亚洲是受气候灾害影响最严重的地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asia-is-most-climate-disaster-impacted-region-un-meteorological-agency-says-2024-04-23/</link><description>世界气象组织（WMO）表示，去年亚洲是世界上受气候相关灾害影响最严重的地区，其中洪水和风暴造成的伤亡人数最多。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asia-is-most-climate-disaster-impacted-region-un-meteorological-agency-says-2024-04-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>